Dialogue: 1,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.51,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,待ってよ　ねぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:41.15,0:00:42.36,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,いない
Dialogue: 1,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.36,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィ　どこ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.94,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,お　あれ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.49,0:00:48.86,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ドアが開かない
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.63,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ダメ　全然電波入らない
Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.13,0:01:04.04,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ルルのは
Dialogue: 1,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.50,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,つながりません
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.38,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,窓も全く開かない
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.01,0:01:11.51,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,どうなってるんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.76,0:01:16.18,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィ　どこに行っちゃったの
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.06,0:01:26.36,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.36,0:01:29.15,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,今　カップが勝手に
Dialogue: 1,0:01:29.15,0:01:30.19,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.13,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,分かった
Dialogue: 1,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.55,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,二人とも　こっち来て
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.30,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.30,0:01:50.01,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,なに
Dialogue: 1,0:01:51.22,0:01:54.34,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ねぇねぇ　私分かっちゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.14,0:01:58.10,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,これ　ドッキリだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.31,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ドッキリですか
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.31,0:02:02.35,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.44,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,きっとテレビの企画で　私たちがかけられる側なの
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.69,0:02:11.49,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,手が混んでるし　ARSテレビがまたやってるのかも
Dialogue: 1,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.99,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ここでリアクションできれば　人気もアップ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.95,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,だから二人も自然に　いい感じに頼むね
Dialogue: 1,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.75,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,これ　そういうんじゃないと思うけど
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.84,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,私はもう一度一階を探すから　二人は上をお願い
Dialogue: 1,0:02:30.17,0:02:33.47,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,やあ　怖いー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.22,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,なにが　起きてるのー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.47,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,こんなの　私耐えられないー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.89,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィはどこー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.52,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,と　塔子さん
Dialogue: 1,0:02:44.52,0:02:48.19,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,出てきてー
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.98,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ドッキリ
Dialogue: 1,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.53,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ホントかな
Dialogue: 1,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.57,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,とりあえず行こっか
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.45,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.26,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,見間違い
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.26,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ルル
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.22,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Comment: 1,0:04:56.11,0:04:59.11,main-JP,,0,0,0,,main
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.99,main-JP,Phone,0,0,0,,電話番号は現在使われておりません
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.49,main-JP,Phone,0,0,0,,もう一度お確かめの上　おかけ直しください
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.08,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,ダメか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:13.92,0:05:15.96,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,お客さんどこまで
Dialogue: 1,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.55,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,海沿いに白いコテージあるでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.97,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,他のホテルとは離れているとこ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.47,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,あそこまでお願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.34,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,ええ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.01,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,うん　なんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.56,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,あ　いいえ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.06,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,お客さん
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.40,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,あんなところに何のようです
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.73,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,あんなところ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.11,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,出るんですよ　あの建物
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.74,0:05:43.16,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,出るって　おバケとか
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.16,0:05:46.74,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,そう　このあたりでは有名なんですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.33,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,あんまり近づかない方がいいと思うけど
Dialogue: 1,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.79,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,そうなの
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.42,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,リリィ　どこ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.05,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,いたら返事して
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.81,0:06:19.03,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,本当にドッキリだったらさ　社長も共犯なのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.32,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,分かりません
Dialogue: 1,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.53,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ここ借りるときすごい安かったって
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.33,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,あれも仕込みだったのかも
Dialogue: 1,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.62,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ったく　いつもポケットしてるくせに
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.59,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,リリィ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.26,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,いないですね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.65,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ちゃんと片付けといてほしいね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.86,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ですね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.86,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ここにもいませんね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.12,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,どこに行ったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.71,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.21,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ルル　お芝居できる
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.21,0:07:25.59,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,いえ　そういうのは私
Dialogue: 1,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.84,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,そっか　私も
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.89,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,どうするかな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.43,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,なんか話そう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.65,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,黙ってると　また仕掛けられそうで嫌だし
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.44,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あの　来てもいいですか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.28,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.53,0:07:50.66,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,アイドルは塔子さんの夢なんですよね
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.16,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,あ　昨日の話
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.12,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい　気になってしまって
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.17,0:08:02.63,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,それじゃ　世奈さんの夢は何ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.01,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,それは
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.18,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子が私を　連れ出してくれたんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.18,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,連れ出して
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.93,0:08:19.19,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,私服とかダンスは好きだけどそれだけだし
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.73,0:08:23.77,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,将来何しようとか　全然考えてなかったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.86,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,そしたら　塔子がいきなり言ったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.57,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,アイドルやろうって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.16,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そうだったんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.62,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,うん　こっちの話も聞かずに
Dialogue: 1,0:08:36.62,0:08:40.50,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,世奈となら絶対なれるから二人でやろうって
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.29,0:08:46.26,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,勝手でしょ　なのに私もその気になっちゃったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:47.67,0:08:50.80,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,まるで　魔法をかけられたみたいに
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.18,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,わかる気がします
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.85,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,今度は何
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.15,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,足音が
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.20,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,なに今の音
Dialogue: 1,0:09:15.66,0:09:16.49,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,斧
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.97,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,あの　まだ着かないんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.72,0:09:36.10,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,走ってるんだけどね
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.73,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,これ以上進めないんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.39,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,はっ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.23,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.15,main-JP,Driver,0,0,0,,{\an8}進めないんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.74,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,えっなに
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.87,0:10:00.70,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,いやこれ　絶対ドッキリなんかじゃないでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.04,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,じゃあ　なんなんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.46,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,心霊現象
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.34,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,停電　直った
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.39,0:10:21.98,main-JP,Rin,0,0,0,,さあここからはいたずらクッキングの時間です
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.94,0:10:26.48,main-JP,Rin,0,0,0,,本日ご紹介するのは　こちら
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.24,main-JP,Rin,0,0,0,,新人アイドルの４人です
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.66,main-JP,Rin,0,0,0,,あ　もうすぐ完成ですよ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.08,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,何これ
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.30,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ちょっと待って
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.60,0:11:04.60,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,確かに私もずっと探してたんですけど
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.27,0:11:09.48,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,どこにもカメラなんてなかったんです
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.40,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,だよね
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.99,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,これって本当にどき
Dialogue: 1,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.66,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,塔子さん
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.46,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.88,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,なんだこいつら
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.89,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子が危ない　下に行ってくる
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.80,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,世奈さん待って
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.43,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.31,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,塔子さん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.54,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,また縫いぐるみ　なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.09,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,怖いね　楽しいね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.51,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,次はどっちにしようかな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.77,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,くそ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.35,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ルル
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.11,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,世奈さん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.57,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,ルルは逃げて　助けを呼ぶの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.08,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,そんな　世奈さんは
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.50,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,いいの　私は塔子を探すから
Dialogue: 1,0:12:52.08,0:12:55.09,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,私たちが戻らなくても　アイドルは続けてよ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.34,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,世奈さん
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.84,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,こんの
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.30,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,世奈さん　世奈さん
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.60,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,もう　ヤダ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.09,0:13:39.84,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,えっ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.47,0:13:48.47,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,そうだ　私あの縫いぐるみに連れられて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.94,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,うぐいすがいない　どこなの
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.98,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,{\an8}ここから出して
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.23,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,{\an8}お願いだったら　もうやめて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.52,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.24,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,やめて　来ないでよ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.50,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,誰か助けて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.63,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,リリレラ　パリレラ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.38,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,お願い　ルルちゃんを助けて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.55,0:15:00.96,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やった
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.57,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,もうダメ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.69,0:15:27.91,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,でも　みんなまだあそこに残されてる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.00,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,トーレ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.43,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,家に帰る
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.45,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私戻らないと
Dialogue: 1,0:16:11.37,0:16:11.95,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.46,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あれで
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.33,0:16:23.30,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,もしかして　今までのことで全部魔法だったの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:27.09,0:16:27.97,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,デット
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.36,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ルルリラ　プルリラ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.03,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ぽっぷんパーム
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.86,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,みんなを助ける力を貸して
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.08,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,これで戦えってこと
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.80,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,ほら　怖いだろ　もっと逃げろ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.80,0:17:55.03,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,飛べちゃうぞ　コロー　 コロー
Dialogue: 1,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.27,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,こいつをやっつけたら
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.98,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,次は逃げた子をいじめてやる
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.81,0:18:06.86,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ねえ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.44,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,なんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.94,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ねえ言いたら
Dialogue: 1,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.45,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,うるさいな　今いいとこな…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.45,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,あなた　魔法の国の人なの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.75,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,ううう　そうそうそうそう
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.25,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,何してるの
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.75,0:18:29.21,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,うっ何って　遊んでたんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.26,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,人間って怖いの好きでしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.88,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,だから　喜ぶと思って
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.88,0:18:38.18,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,お願い　全部元通りにして　今すぐに
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.14,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,はい　ごめんなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.69,main-JP,Creature,0,0,0,,じゃあ　そういうことね
Dialogue: 1,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.82,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,いやぁ　来ないでぇ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.20,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,止まった
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.13,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ここどこ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.13,0:19:10.71,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.71,0:19:14.42,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,世奈　ねこれドッキリ　ドッキリだよね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.97,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,わかんないけど　終わったみたい
Dialogue: 1,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.31,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,リリィさん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.44,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,ルルちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.81,0:19:31.94,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,よかった　世奈さんも塔子さんも無事だったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.95,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい　こんなことになって
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.28,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,私も何が起こったのかわかんないんだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.74,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,心霊現象だよ　多分
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.20,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,幽霊ってやつ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.71,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,幽霊　あれは…
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.46,0:19:48.71,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,な、なんだろうね
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.71,0:19:54.05,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,考えてもなかった　私以外に魔法を使う人がいたなんて
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.97,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,っていうか　この後どうする
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.97,0:20:01.56,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,さすがに合宿再開ってわけにもいかないよね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.48,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,バーベキューやろうよ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.44,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,え?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.86,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やらないの
Dialogue: 1,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.74,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,いや　やりたいけど
Dialogue: 1,0:20:14.74,0:20:18.74,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,じゃあやろうよ　最後は絶対楽しい方がいいもん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.62,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,やろっか　バーベキュー
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.66,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,そうだね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.37,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい!
Dialogue: 1,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.16,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,やったー
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.87,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,おーい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.79,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,みんな　大丈夫か
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.55,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,ダークシーがさ　ぐるぐるぐるぐる回っちゃって
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.22,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,なんか持ってる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.55,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,浄霊グッズでしょうか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.27,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,はい　肉
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.06,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,はーい
Dialogue: 1,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.39,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,ほんと　気をつけてよね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:49.39,0:20:52.36,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,お前も値段見て大喜びだっただろうが
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.36,0:20:53.32,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,そうだけど
Dialogue: 1,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.28,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,おかわりください
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.69,main-JP,Yasuo,0,0,0,,はいはい　焼けてるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.91,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,リリィはいつも通りだね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.91,0:21:03.78,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,ですね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.50,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,閉じ込められた時のお話
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.71,0:21:09.29,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,え
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.71,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,なんか　変なこと話しちゃったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.80,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子には言わないで
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.67,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,どうしてですか
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.05,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,恥ずかしいじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.31,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,わかりました
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.81,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,約束ね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:28.18,0:21:28.89,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.77,0:21:32.56,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,私　アイドル続けますね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.57,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,言うね
Dialogue: 1,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.49,main-JP,Toko,0,0,0,,{\an8}あリリィ　それ私のお肉
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.49,0:21:42.16,main-JP,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\an8}塔子さん　ピーマン食べないと
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.90,0:21:44.95,main-JP,Sena,0,0,0,,行こう　のんびりしてるとあの二人に全部食べられるよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.95,0:21:45.58,main-JP,Rui,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.44,main-JP,Azuki,0,0,0,,あげて
Dialogue: 1,0:22:15.44,0:22:17.69,main-JP,Uguisu,0,0,0,,ここから出せ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.36,main-JP,Uguisu/Azuki,0,0,0,,なんか　忘れてない
Comment: 0,0:00:24.42,0:00:27.42,main-CN,,0,0,0,,beforeop
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.42,0:00:29.05,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,你要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.51,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,等等我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.15,0:00:42.36,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.36,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,莉莉 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.94,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,诶 啊嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.49,0:00:48.86,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,门打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:02.63,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,不行 完全收不到信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.13,0:01:04.04,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,露露你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.50,0:01:06.50,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,也是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:09.38,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,窗户也全都打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:11.51,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.76,0:01:16.18,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,莉莉 到底去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:26.36,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:29.15,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,刚刚 杯子自己动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:30.19,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:46.13,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:48.55,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,两位 快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.55,0:01:49.30,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.30,0:01:50.01,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.22,0:01:54.34,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,呐呐 我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.14,0:01:58.10,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,这种情况是「整蛊节目」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.72,0:02:01.31,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,整蛊吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.31,0:02:02.35,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.35,0:02:06.44,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,肯定是电视台的企划 而我们是被整的一方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.69,0:02:11.49,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,手法这么精细 说不定又是 ARS 电视台在搞鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.99,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,在这里有很好的反应 肯定会人气爆棚的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.95,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,所以拜托两位也要自然点 留下好影响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:21.75,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,我感觉这应该不是你说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:28.84,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,我再去一楼找一圈 楼上就拜托你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:33.47,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,呀 我好怕怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.84,0:02:36.22,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,发生 什么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.22,0:02:39.47,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,这种场面 我受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.89,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,莉莉你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:44.52,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,塔 塔子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:48.19,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,快出来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:49.98,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,整蛊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.53,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:54.57,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,总之我们先上楼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:02:59.45,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.42,0:03:14.26,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,看错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:15.26,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:18.22,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我来啦
Comment: 0,0:04:56.11,0:04:59.11,main-CN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:02.99,main-CN,Phone,0,0,0,,您好 您拨打的号码暂未启用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:06.49,main-CN,Phone,0,0,0,,请核对后再拨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:09.08,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:15.96,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,您要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.55,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,海岸边不是有间白色别墅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.97,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,和其他的酒店距离较远
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:22.47,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,请载我到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.47,0:05:23.34,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.01,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.01,0:05:27.56,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,啊 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.06,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,这位乘客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.40,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,你去那个地方做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.94,0:05:35.73,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.27,0:05:39.11,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,那座建筑 闹鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:43.16,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,闹鬼 是有怪物吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:46.74,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,是的 在我们这片还挺出名的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.74,0:05:50.33,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,我认为还是不要靠太近为好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.37,0:05:54.79,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:05:59.42,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,莉莉 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.05,0:06:06.05,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,听到了快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:19.03,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,如果真是整蛊节目 社长或许也是共犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.32,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:25.53,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,租用这里的时候听说很便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:27.33,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,或许也是事先准备好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.83,0:06:30.62,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,真的是 明明一直双手插兜不作为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.63,0:06:40.59,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.26,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.36,0:07:00.65,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,真希望她能好好收拾下房间
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:01.86,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.86,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,她也不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.12,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,到底去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.96,0:07:17.71,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,被关起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.21,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,露露 你还能演下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:25.59,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,这个我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:28.84,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,这样啊 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.89,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:35.43,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,来聊聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:39.65,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,要是保持沉默 或又会被讨厌的东西整蛊了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.44,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那个 我问问你可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:45.28,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,问什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.53,0:07:50.66,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,偶像是塔子姐的梦想对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.16,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,啊 昨天的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.54,0:07:58.12,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是的 我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.17,0:08:02.63,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那么 世奈姐的梦想是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:05.01,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:12.18,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,是塔子把我拯救出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:14.18,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:19.19,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,虽然我喜欢衣着和跳舞 但也仅限于此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.73,0:08:23.77,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,将来到底要做什么 完全没有想过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.57,0:08:27.86,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,然后 塔子她突然就说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.86,0:08:29.57,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,「来当偶像吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.20,0:08:32.16,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,原来是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:36.62,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,嗯 连我的意见也不问问
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:40.50,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,「世奈的话绝对能做成 我们两人一起吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:46.26,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,很任性对吧 但是我也开始信以为真了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:50.80,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,简直 就像被施展了魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.18,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.85,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,这次又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:02.15,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:12.20,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,刚刚的是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:16.49,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,斧头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.55,0:09:32.97,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,那个 还没有到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.72,0:09:36.10,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,确实在前进
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.73,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,但一直进不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:41.39,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.23,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:45.15,main-CN,Driver,0,0,0,,{\an8}完全进不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.74,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,诶怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:10:00.70,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,不对 这个绝对不是整蛊节目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.70,0:10:03.04,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那么 会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.46,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,灵异现象
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:12.34,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,停电 修好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.39,0:10:21.98,main-CN,Rin,0,0,0,,那么接下来 轮到我们的「整蛊烹饪」环节啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:26.48,main-CN,Rin,0,0,0,,今天向大家介绍的是她们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:31.24,main-CN,Rin,0,0,0,,四位新人偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:36.66,main-CN,Rin,0,0,0,,啊 已经基本完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:39.08,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:52.30,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,等会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.60,0:11:04.60,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,的确 我从刚刚开始就一直在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:09.48,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,无论哪里都没有摄影机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.40,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.16,0:11:18.99,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,这真的是整蛊节目…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.66,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,塔子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:27.46,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.54,0:11:32.88,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,这些家伙是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:37.89,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子很危险 我们快下楼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:39.80,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,世奈姐等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.43,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:44.31,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,塔子姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.66,0:12:03.54,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,又是玩偶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.09,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,很害怕吧 很快乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:14.51,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,下一个选谁好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.60,0:12:25.77,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.35,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,露露
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.11,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,世奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.07,0:12:41.57,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,露露你快跑 快点找人求助
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.08,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,怎么这样 世奈姐你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.50,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,我没事的 我会在这里找塔子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:55.09,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,就算我们回不去了 你也要把偶像继续做下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.09,0:12:56.34,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,世奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.84,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,你们这群…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.30,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,世奈姐 世奈姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.60,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,已经 不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.09,0:13:39.84,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:48.47,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,对了 我被那个玩偶带了过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.10,0:13:52.94,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,豌豆不在 它去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.98,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,{\an8}快点从这里出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.23,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,{\an8}拜托了 快点住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.36,0:13:57.52,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,露露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:07.24,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,不要 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.62,0:14:09.50,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,谁能救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.79,0:14:16.63,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,莉莉露菈 啪礼露菈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.38,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,拜托了 帮帮露露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.55,0:15:00.96,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.28,0:15:22.57,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:27.91,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,但是 大家还都在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.13,0:15:42.00,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,解除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.18,0:15:48.43,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我想回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:06.45,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,但我必须回去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:11.95,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.21,0:16:17.46,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:23.30,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,难不成 至今为止的意外都是魔法造成的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:27.97,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,黛特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:48.36,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,露露莉菈 蒲露莉菈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.03,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,啵硼帕姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.40,0:17:24.86,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,借我帮助大家的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:36.08,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,要用这个战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.17,0:17:51.80,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,看吧 很恐怖的 快点逃跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:55.03,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,要飞起来咯 咕隆咕隆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:59.27,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,干掉这家伙之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:01.98,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,就去欺负逃跑的那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.81,0:18:06.86,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.86,0:18:08.44,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.94,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我在叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:14.45,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,好吵 我现在正在…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.45,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,你是魔法之国的人对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.75,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,啊嗯 我是是是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:25.25,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:29.21,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,嗯做什么 当然是玩游戏啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:31.26,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,人类很喜欢恐怖的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.26,0:18:33.88,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,所以我想你们会开心来着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:38.18,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,拜托 现在立刻马上恢复如初
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.14,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,好的 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:44.69,main-CN,Creature,0,0,0,,那么 就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:54.82,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不要 不要过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:01.20,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,停下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.13,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,这是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:10.71,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,塔子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:14.42,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,世奈 这是整蛊 整蛊对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:19.97,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,虽然不知道 但看起来已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:26.31,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.44,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,露露酱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:31.94,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,太好了 世奈姐和塔子姐都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.36,0:19:34.95,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,对不起 在这里发生这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.28,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,其实我自己也搞不清楚到底发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.28,0:19:40.74,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,大概是灵异现象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.20,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,幽灵什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:44.71,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,幽灵 那会是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:48.71,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,会 会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:54.05,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,没想到 除了我之外还有人能使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:57.97,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,说起来 接下来怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:01.56,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,出了这么大的乱子 合宿应该是泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:10.48,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,我们来烧烤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.48,0:20:11.44,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.44,0:20:12.86,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,不做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.86,0:20:14.74,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,不是 虽然想做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.74,0:20:18.74,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,那么就来吧 最后还是要开开心心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.62,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,行吧 烧烤
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.62,0:20:22.66,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.66,0:20:23.37,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:25.16,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:26.87,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.79,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,大家 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.63,0:20:35.55,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,出租车一直都在循环转圈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.22,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,感觉带着什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:41.55,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,驱魔除灵道具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:45.27,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,来 肉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.27,0:20:47.06,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.06,0:20:49.39,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,真的是 你也要多注意点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:52.36,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,你看到价格不也很高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.36,0:20:53.32,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,这确实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.28,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,再来一份
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.69,main-CN,Yasuo,0,0,0,,好好 正在烤制
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.91,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,莉莉还是一如既往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.91,0:21:03.78,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.50,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,被关起来时说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:09.29,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:13.71,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,总感觉我说了些奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.80,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,请不要告诉塔子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.67,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:22.05,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,因为很害羞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.06,0:21:26.31,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.31,0:21:27.81,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.18,0:21:28.89,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.77,0:21:32.56,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,我也会继续当偶像的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.36,0:21:36.57,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,不愧是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:39.49,main-CN,Toko,0,0,0,,{\an8}啊莉莉 那个是我的肉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.49,0:21:42.16,main-CN,Fuu,0,0,0,,{\an8}塔子姐 青椒也得吃呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:44.95,main-CN,Sena,0,0,0,,走吧 再等一会的话她们两个会把肉全吃完的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.95,0:21:45.58,main-CN,Rui,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.35,0:22:15.44,main-CN,Azuki,0,0,0,,快打开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.44,0:22:17.69,main-CN,Uguisu,0,0,0,,快放我们出去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.44,0:22:22.36,main-CN,Uguisu/Azuki,0,0,0,,你们是不是忘记了些什么啊
